dc:description: Rim and neck missing: neck had narrow diameter.  Bulbous round body, with articulated ring base.  Slight bulge in center of base.  Vestige of handle on shoulder.  Light orange clay; brown slip on upper part of body (maybe all over body) and one black spiral motif on shoulder.  Tool mark scraped depression on shoulder.
